gomodel:SYNGO_196  a      owl:Ontology ;
        rdfs:comment      "Rationale: RAB14 was detected on highly purified synaptic vesicles using mass spectrometric and immunoblot analyses. GFP-RAB14 colocalises with synaptophysin puncta in transiently transfected cultured hippocampal neurons.. Experimental description: Legend to Figure 2 \"Enrichment profiles of Rab GTPases on purified SVs isolated from rat brain homogenates, determined by quantitative immunoblotting.\"\n\n20/2/2017 Pim:\nSpecies of Rab14 OE construct used in Fig.3 is not stated in the M&M. Table 1 and Fig.2 are sufficient to claim the selected term, however, and species is set to Rat." , "Automated change 2024-03-14: GO:0098993 replaced by GO:0030672" ;
        lego:modelstate   "production" ;
        dc:contributor    "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-5615-1014" ;
